{"title":"2022 Trek Roscoe 140mm hardtail gets 29″ wheels and longer, lower, slacker geometry","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/29/2022-trek-roscoe-140mm-hardtail-gets-29-wheels-and-longer-lower-slacker-geometry/","date":1627570852000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>The extremely popular Trek Roscoe hardtail mountain bike has received an overhaul for 2022. Upgrading from 27.5″+ to a 29er and rocking a 140mm travel fork, the Roscoe now sports a rather more modern trail geometry… longer, lower, slacker, you get the point, right? There are now 6 sizes available from an XS (which keeps the 27.5″+ wheels) and 29ers running from S-XL, with prices starting from a very affordable $1,699.99. We have everything you need to know about the 2022 Trek Roscoe right here.</p><figure id=\"attachment_266747\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-266747\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb26/ng:webp/ngcb26\" alt=\"kade edwards 2022 trek roscoe 8\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 120w,http