rek-roscoe-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084416/kade-edwards-2022-trek-roscoe-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb26 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-266747\">Kade Edwards’ Trek Roscoe 8; this build retails at $2,299.99 USD</figcaption></figure><p>The 2022 Trek Roscoe is an aluminium hardtail mountain bike, now with a modern trail bike geometry. Its most recent evolution swaps out 27.5″+ wheels for faster rolling 29″ wheels, built around an all-new frame with a more progressive geometry that should improve its descending qualities immeasurably. Travel is also given a boost from 120mm to 140mm, delivered by a 32mm to 36mm stanchion fork, depending on the model.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg\" alt=\"kade edwards riding steep turns 2022 trek roscoe wales\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084422/kade-edwards-riding-2022-trek-roscoe-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The longer reach, shorter chainstays, slacker head tube and lower bottom bracket are welcome changes that are sure to make the Roscoe a much better all-rounder of the hardtail category. Across the XS-XL frame sizes reach has increased ~20mm and the head angle has slackened significantly to 65°.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales.jpg\" alt=\"kade edwards riding 2022 trek roscoe 8\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084409/2022-trek-roscoe-kade-edwards-railing-berms-wales-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Reach on the ML has actually increased massively from 410mm to 455mm. All frame sizes have a straight top tube, with the longer reach allowing for a more gradual angle from the head tube down to the seat tube join. This has actually improved standover as compared to the previous Roscoe. Seat tubes are also slightly shorter, with increased seat post insertion length so that riders can take advantage of a long travel dropper post.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping.jpg\" alt=\"2022 trek roscoe jumping\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084356/2022-trek-roscoe-hardtail-mtb-trail-geomtry-jumping-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-cont