29″ x 2.6″.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance.jpg\" alt=\"2022 trek roscoe tire clearance 29 x 2.6&quot;\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-630x420.jpg 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb26 src ng ngcb26 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/28084436/Trek-Roscoe-tire-clearance-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>For the 2022 Roscoe, Trek have moved away from a proportional frame design with a consistent SA and rear-centre length across the frame sizes.</p><table><tbody><tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td>XS</td><td>S</td><td>M</td><td>ML</td><td>L</td><td>XL</td></tr><tr><td>Wheel Size</td><td>27.5″+</td><td>29″</td><td>29″</td><td>29″</td><td>29″</td><td>29″</td></tr><tr><td>Seat tube length</td><td>340</td><td>360</td><td>420</td><td>435</td><td>450</td><td>500</td></tr><tr><td>Stem length</td><td>40</td><td>40</td><td>50</td><td>50</td><td>50</td><td>50</td></tr><tr><td>Reach</td><td>390.0</td><td>415.0</td><td>440.0</td><td>455.0</td><td>470.0</td><td>495.0</td></tr><tr><td>Stack</td><td>591.5</td><td>625.6</td><td>634.6</td><td>639.2</td><td>643.7</td><td>666.4</td></tr><tr><td>Effective Top Tube</td><td>551.8</td><td>586.1</td><td>613.6</td><td>629.9</td><td>646.1</td><td>677.3</td></tr><tr><td>Chainstay length</td><td>430</td><td>430</td><td>430</td><td>430</td><td>430</td><td>430</td></tr><tr